MY IDEA:

I'd like to map movement within/in and out of London over time, either in terms of public transport/cycling
(perhaps over 1 week, as it will be a lot of data) or migration (over years/decades). If migration, i'd also like to
add some element to my "story" about different cultures in London, e.g. food. I'll get inspiration for interesting London
map visualisations from http://mappinglondon.co.uk/category/data/ and there is some open data about transport in London,
https://tfl.gov.uk/info-for/open-data-users/. Hopefully not too adventurous for me...
